I really, I really loved the ministry.

00:17:31.910 --> 00:17:34.069
I loved the, especially there's a district

00:17:34.069 --> 00:17:37.589
working with the circuit overseer and his wife every week

00:17:37.589 --> 00:17:38.990
and out service.

