She lived alone so she needed care.

00:19:05.549 --> 00:19:07.869
And again, they allowed us this time.

00:19:07.869 --> 00:19:09.190
We went back.

00:19:09.190 --> 00:19:11.509
And just as in the case with my sister,

00:19:11.509 --> 00:19:16.470
