00:19:48.509 --> 00:19:52.950
with my family and experiences, shared experiences.

00:19:52.950 --> 00:19:55.509
And we felt good that we had been

00:19:55.509 --> 00:19:58.990
able to help these people that had been mentors for us.

00:19:58.990 --> 00:19:59.750
Yes.

00:19:59.750 --> 00:20:03.630
So loyalty to your family, loyalty to Jehovah.

