I was assigned to the alterations department,

00:20:16.589 --> 00:20:18.269
the sewing department.

00:20:18.269 --> 00:20:22.190
And recently, before that sister,

00:20:22.190 --> 00:20:24.269
Gertrude and her husband, Martin Putsinger,

00:20:24.269 --> 00:20:25.710
had been called into Bethel.

00:20:25.710 --> 00:20:27.950
And he was a member of the governing body.

00:20:27.950 --> 00:20:29.990
And she had been trained under a tailor.

00:20:29.990 --> 00:20:32.589
So she was excellent in alterations.

