00:23:53.789 --> 00:23:58.190
and they said, we're going to take you out to a midnight colony.

00:23:58.190 --> 00:24:01.950
And so I left at 8 and I didn't get back to 11 o'clock at night.

00:24:01.950 --> 00:24:05.549
And I was a little bit disturbed about that hour, that late or getting back.

00:24:05.549 --> 00:24:07.589
Well, you see, it's a midnight community.

00:24:07.589 --> 00:24:11.190
