00:24:25.630 --> 00:24:28.589
September 1st, issue of the watchtower

00:24:28.589 --> 00:24:31.630
about this family of men and nights that came into the truth.

00:24:31.630 --> 00:24:35.390
And now the work is spreading like wildfire among the men and nights.

00:24:35.390 --> 00:24:41.069
